Source: glxosd
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Nick Guletskii <nick@nickguletskii.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), cmake, libgl1-mesa-dev, libglu1-mesa-dev, mesa-common-dev, libfontconfig1-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.6
Section: utils
Homepage: https://glxosd.nickguletskii.com/
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/nickguletskii/GLXOSD
